(23, 2, 'en', 'Privacy Policy', '<p><br></p><p>This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which HomeIQ Electromechanical Services LLC (\"The Company\") collects, uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users (each, a \"User\") of the HOMEIQ.AE website (\"Site\"). This privacy policy applies to the Site and all products and services offered by HomeIQ Electromechanical Services LLC.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>SECTION 1 - WHAT DO WE DO WITH YOUR INFORMATION?</strong></p><p>When you purchase something from our website, as part of the buying and selling process, we collect the personal information you give us such as your name, address and email address.<br>When you browse&nbsp;our website, we also automatically receive your computer’s internet protocol (IP) address in order to provide us with information that helps us learn about your browser and operating system.</p><p>Email marketing :With your permission, we may send you emails about our store, new products and other updates.</p><p>We adopt generally accepted industry standards for the protection of the personal information that you submit, both during transmission and after receipt. However, although we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your personal information, we do not guarantee the security of any of your private transmissions against unauthorized or unlawful interception or access by third parties.</p><p><br></p><p><strong>SECTION 2 - CONSENT</strong></p><p>When you provide us with personal information to complete a transaction, place an order, arrange for an installation, delivery or return a purchase, we imply that you consent to our collecting it and using it for that specific reason only.</p><p>If we ask for your personal information for a secondary reason, like marketing, we will either ask you directly for your expressed consent, or provide you with an opportunity to say no.</p><p>Withdraw of consent</p><p>If after you opt-in, you change your mind, you may withdraw your